      <p>Your training allows you to use the Mastery properties of two kinds of weapons with which you are proficient. You can change the chosen kinds whenever you finish a Long Rest.</p>
    </description>
    <sheet>
      <description>You can use the Mastery property of two proficient weapon kinds; you can change them on a Long Rest.</description>
    </sheet>
  </element>

